author: akarasulu
msg: Took out getReverseCursor() without arguments because it does the same
thing that a forward cursor does except with result sets returned in
BigInteger ascending order rather than String value order.  Otherwise it
just confuses users.  For the time being it has been commented out.  If
needed it can be reinstated.  If it is not used within the next couple
of releases it can be removed completely.
